ing: 1/3 cup bittersweet chocolate chips, melted (see Tip)
des: "These easy, chocolate-dipped gingersnaps are topped with a sprinkling of crystallized ginger and dried cranberries."
ins: Dip gingersnaps into melted chocolate. Let the excess drip off. Place on a wax paper-lined plate. Sprinkle with crystallized ginger and cranberries. Refrigerate until the chocolate is set, about 30 minutes.
